      "text": "都会の喧噪を忘れてのんびり過ごすのもいいわね\n温泉街も風情があって素敵だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nice to forget the hustle and bustle of the city and relax.\nThis hot spring town has such a charming atmosphere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
