      "text": "老朽化してひび割れた壁とか、手入れされずに\n雑草が伸び放題の寂れた雰囲気とか、たまらないわね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The old‚ cracked walls and overgrown weeds give it\nan desolate feel‚ which is irresistible~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
