      "text": "そんなこと言って、耳まで赤くなってるじゃないか\nもしかして照れてるのか？　遙子は可愛いな――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that‚ but even your ears are red. Are you embarrassed?\nAre you embarrassed? Haruko is so cute――",
        "id": ""
      },
