      "text": "{user}君って意外と意地悪なのね\nからかうつもりが、からかわれちゃったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun‚ you're surprisingly mischievous.\nI tried to tease you‚ but I ended up being teased instead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
